    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>地球遭到了克苏鲁的攻击</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯一能保护我们的就是我们心爱的猫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演你最喜欢的宠物，用毛线、水果和其他美食武装自己。穿上最时尚的服装，向克苏鲁展示为什么猫统治世界。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特征</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >十几只猫可供选择</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每只猫都有独特的属性。了解它们的优点和缺点，并相应地调整你的构造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/83303ee5342501f09ef70c65e702727b.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >给自己买一些舒适且功能强大的东西</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 提高你的攻击速度，提高你的耐力或释放彩虹的力量！升级，人们，升级！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/f97c55099eb79e8e78f3583764a2b423.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >爱的注入</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吃掉你的武器来获得永久的增益。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/2591af218418ef4eb571a80d8df3afe2.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/2591af218418ef4eb571a80d8df3afe2.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/2591af218418ef4eb571a80d8df3afe2.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >元进程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在与克苏鲁战斗时，你会收集纸板，然后可以用它们来购买新的猫或竞技场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/9a13ad0c2192ddfcecda6507e3502f1f.poster.avif?t=1736148027\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/9a13ad0c2192ddfcecda6507e3502f1f.webm?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270620/extras/9a13ad0c2192ddfcecda6507e3502f1f.mp4?t=1736148027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
